# TraderLab‚Ñ¢ Security Layer

This folder contains **screenshot and screen recording protection** for Android & iOS.  

- Android: Prevents screenshots & recording (shows black screen).
- iOS: Detects screenshots, blurs the screen, and closes session.

‚ö†Ô∏è These modules are **dormant** and not yet integrated with `TraderLab.py`.  
They will be **activated on November 09, 2025**.

// TraderLab‚Ñ¢ Secure Layer - Dormant until 09 Nov 2025

import UIKit

class SecureViewController: UIViewController {
    override func viewDidLoad() {
        super.viewDidLoad()
        // üö® Screenshot detection
        NotificationCenter.default.addObserver(
            self,
            selector: #selector(userDidScreenshot),
            name: UIApplication.userDidTakeScreenshotNotification,
            object: nil
        )
    }

    @objc func userDidScreenshot() {
        // Blur + optional logout
        let blur = UIVisualEffectView(effect: UIBlurEffect(style: .dark))
        blur.frame = view.bounds
        view.addSubview(blur)

        DispatchQueue.main.asyncAfter(deadline: .now() + 1.5) {
            exit(0) // terminate session
        }
    }
}

